div.p:
It is a Metaphor taken from young Impes; 
                  Anſw. 
                I will plant them, that is, I will make them to take roote there; and that is, where they and their ſoyle agree well together, when they are well and ſufficiently provided for, as a plant ſuckes nouriſhment from the ſoyle that fitteth it.
